Texts.Chs: 多年来第一次收到来报。不是地球，而是一个自称是鲛人的人，说他们在我们的门外，外面真的很冷。我不会上当的。忽视它。
Texts.Eng: Received communication for the first time in years. Wasn't Earth, but someone claiming to be a Hylotl, saying they were outside our door and it was really cold outside. Not falling for that one. Ignored it.

Texts.Chs: 还是不明白他们怎么知道我们的传输频率。
Texts.Eng: Still confused how they knew our transmission frequency.
